701181f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 192nd Street (East)
701181f-a.text:
2562 and 2560 Grand Concourse, at, and adjoining the S.E. corner
of E. 192nd Street.
May 16, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.

701180f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 192nd Street (East)
701180f-a.text:
2550 Grand Concourse, south of the S.E. corner of East 192nd Street. The house is at this date (1938) no longer in existence; its site being
occupied by a 1-story brick building.
About 1913.
